====
PONG
====
By: Alvin Chua

Super simple Pong clone made with SDL. Borrowed some overall game organization/design from "Reconstructing Cave Story" by Christopher Hebert (can be found at https://github.com/chebert/cavestory-screencast).

CONTROLS:
P1: W/S
P2: Up/Down

